Tittle:- To create a PHP script that stores multiple values in an array and displays them on a web page.

Program-   


<!DOCTYPE html> 
<html> 
<head> 
<title>PHP Array Example</title> 
</head> 
<body> 
<h1>Student Subjects</h1> 
<?php 
$subjects = array("Mathematics", "Physics", "Computer 
Science", "Electronics", "English"); 
echo "<h3>Subjects List:</h3>"; 
foreach ($subjects as $value) { 
echo $value . "<br>"; 
} 
?> 
</body> 
</html>
